high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spoon with the blue handle on the right side of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink by the window.
Put the spoon inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on the left.
Put the rinsed spoon in front of the coffee maker to the right of the green sponge on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spoon on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Clean the ladle in the sink.
Place the ladle on the counter, to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean ladle on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and remove it.
Step to the right to face the counter.
Place the ladle on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To wash a ladle and place it on the counter by the sink.
